(203, 1, '2016-06-12 18:58:55', '2016-06-12 11:58:55', '<img src="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/kru-stephane-1-e1463928240388.jpg" width="520" height="669" srcset="" class="so-widget-image">\r\n<p><span style="color: #ffff00;">Muay Sukhothai Camp was established in XXXX by Kru (master) Stephane Magoutier, who has been learning Muay Thai for more than 25 years. Kru Stephane is certified through World Muay Thai Association and Federation in Thailand and International. He is also widely recognized as Muay Thai practitioner, trainer, judge and referee by international and national fighting championship in both Indonesia and France. His passion and love for Muay Thai has led him to start the International Muaythai Organization and Muay Sukhothai Camp in Bandung. </span></p>\r\n<p>where people can learn Muay Thai, Bushido, Fit Thai, and Urban Defence.&nbsp;He also opened the Muay Sukhothai Academy where students can polish and&nbsp;learn&nbsp;advanced techniques and graduate with&nbsp;international certificates as&nbsp;Muay Thai instructors.</p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #ffff00;">His experiences led him to develop Fithai as his reference for students whose their goal is to loss their weight and gain the stamina. These references has gave a 100% satisfaction to the students that follow his rules.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '83-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-12 18:58:55', '2016-06-12 11:58:55', '', 83, 'http://localhost/muaysukhothai/2016/06/12/83-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
