(300, 1, '2016-06-13 13:19:23', '2016-06-13 06:19:23', '&nbsp;\r\n<img src="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo.png" width="700" height="204" srcset="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo.png 700w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo-300x87.png 300w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo-230x67.png 230w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo-350x102.png 350w" class="so-widget-image">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<img src="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/kru-stephane.jpg" width="500" height="750" srcset="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/kru-stephane.jpg 500w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/kru-stephane-200x300.jpg 200w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/kru-stephane-230x345.jpg 230w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/kru-stephane-350x525.jpg 350w" class="so-widget-image">\r\n<p><span style="color: #ffffff;"><span class="mty-title">MUAY SUKHOTHAI CAMP</span> was established in XXXX by Kru (master) Stephane Magoutier, who has been learning Muay Thai for more than 25 years. Kru Stephane is certified through World Muay Thai Association and Federation in Thailand and International. He is also widely recognized as Muay Thai practitioner, trainer, judge and referee by international and national fighting championship in both Indonesia and France. His passion and love for Muay Thai has led him to start the International Muaythai Organization and Muay Sukhothai Camp in Bandung. </span></p>\r\n<strong><span style="color: #ffffff;">Kru Stephane Magoutier Biography:</span></strong><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Kru (master) Muaythai 11 Khan level from Thailand-Europe</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Representative World I.M.O (Inter Muaythai Organization)</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Founder Muay-Sukhothai Camp Bandung Indonesia</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Coach National Team Muaythai Indonesia</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Expert Instructor Special Force Army and Tactics Police</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Founder of C1 pro (world fighting organisation)</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Champion Muaythai Sogn Sukhothai Phan Thailand</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Champion Muaythai Asia-Pacific Series 1</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- Champion Muaythai France FMT</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- 25 Years of Experience in Muaythai</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- 15 years of experience in Coaching</span><br>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">- 16 years of experience in Special Force Army and Bodyguard</span>\r\n<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">At Muay Sukhothai camp, it is our best interest to ensure every students&nbsp;receive&nbsp;undivided attention. Our coach and trainers&nbsp;will guide you with details and help you speed your learning process. <span class="mty-title">MUAY THAI, FIT THAI, BUSHIDO, URBAN DEFENSE </span>are some of the programs that we&nbsp;offer at&nbsp;Muay Sukhothai&nbsp;Camp. We also offer <span class="mty-title">THE&nbsp;ACADEMY </span>program for those who .......... Some of our&nbsp;programs are only available at our Base Camp, but we are planning on expanding in the near future. We offer different programs at different locations. For details on&nbsp;our programs&nbsp;and schedule, please check out the <a>Programs</a> and <a>Schedule</a>&nbsp;page.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean ornare nec arcu ut maximus. Maecenas eleifend odio turpis, eu tincidunt metus accumsan sed. Donec pulvinar est id pharetra hendrerit. Vivamus scelerisque augue nisi, a vulputate tortor viverra at. Mauris hendrerit tristique commodo. Proin id lib