(320, 1, '2016-06-17 10:09:13', '2016-06-17 03:09:13', '<h2 class="mty-header mty-underline yellow" style="text-align: center;">INTERNATIONAL MUAY THAI CAMP</h2>\r\nHereÂ at International Muay Sukhothai Camp, our goal is to help students and members achieve practicalÂ and legitimate results.Â Our instructors have undergone extensive training in both Muay Thai and Fit Thai and are personallyÂ handpickedÂ by Kru Stephane Magoutier.Â In this camp, we ensure that you receive world-class training from a dedicated, loyal and talented staff.\r\n<h6 style="text-align: center;">SUPPORTED BY:</h6>\r\n<img class="so-widget-image" src="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo.png" srcset="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo.png 700w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo-300x87.png 300w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo-230x67.png 230w, http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/world-logo-350x102.png 350w" width="700" height="204" />\r\n\r\nMUAY MUAY MUAY\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span class="mty-header mty-underline" style="color: white; border-bottom-color: #D1DC2F;">PROGRAMS</span></h2>\r\n<img src="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/try-2.png" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><span style="color: #ffffff;">MUAY THAI</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">Muay Thai is a great martial art for self-defense. It is the art of 8 limbs using Thai boxing, and utilizing elbow strikes, knee strikes and kicks as weapons. It is suitable for children, women and men to learn and it has gained global popularity.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.google.com"><span class="roll-button"> VIEW SCHEDULE </span></a> <img src="http://localhost/muaysukhothai/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/try-2.png" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><span style="color: #ffffff;">MUAY THAI ACADEMY</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #ffffff;">Lorem Ipsum is si